Description:
Steelwish are industry leaders in the design, manufacturer, supply of:

• Bespoke cycle parking racks;
• Bicycle indoor trainers, scooter racks;
• Flooring safety products including tactile indicators, mats and stair nosings;
• Carpark fitouts including over bonnet box, bollard and wheel stops.

Standard Products
As designers and manufacturers of our own products, we are able to offer quick turn-around times, unrivalled flexibility and the highest quality products. Our 24/7 call centre is managed by industry professionals with excellent product knowledge. Should you need any advice on the choice or suitability of a particular product, our team are more than willing to help.

Our core purpose is to inspire and enable more sustainable communities. We are committed to changing the way we think about bike parking and infrastructure. Bike parking is highly visible and a reflection of your commitment to a greener environment. Designated parking is more orderly for buildings, prevents damage to trees and street furniture and prevents bikes from blocking walkways. Our products serve to encourage alternative transportation while enhancing the appearance of your grounds and your image. 

Welcome to send your inquiry to sales@steelwish.com
